SV Chrome Hotel is a boutique hotel poised to bring Spanish hospitality to Nigeria. We are currently recruiting to fill the vacant position below: Job Title: Mixologist Location: Abuja Job Descriptions Duties and Responsibilities
Mixologists have specific job duties and often focus on certain types of alcohol and cocktails depending on where they work, but the core duties of mixologists are the same across all companies, breweries, and distilleries. These duties include: Mixing Drinks: Entertain and Educate Guests: Design New Beverage Menu Items: Clean and Organize Bar: Maintain Alcohol Inventory: Follow Alcohol Laws: Make Drink Suggestions: Prepare Garnishes: Skills and Qualifications Application Closing Date
